➜听尘居士：秋语寂寂星有声
http://www.sohu.com/a/418852428_100115135	50943
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/4548028a350244c6baf3f8d0d4e7a07e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋语寂寂星有声</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/听尘居士</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心对秋风花欲语，意染红叶月无声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长空垂暮山悬色，大漠落霞水含情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我上楼台思见影，鸟归故林百味空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乾坤无边滔滔浪，天地有界暗暗星。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/2bd73fac91454a3fb4db903fbf568ab2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>听尘居士，原名牛喜忠。吉林籍，现居深圳。半生无所成，流浪江湖。偶弄笔墨，未有一名。闲了拈花惹草，迎来半院春色；静时参禅打坐，佛道一通乱修。朋友小聚可品香茗，饮自酿美酒，临厨而成美食。唯不懂人间烟火，只好浪迹天涯一隅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/5685c378123546b19c939155b9c93be7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
