➜江西诗人时差先生：镜子与墙
http://www.sohu.com/a/418853031_100115135	51238
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ad83623b098f48958e2df75e22e429df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>镜子与墙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过是一道墙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白洁得自以为是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对面的镜子把它看在眼里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">镜子却成了一张白纸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肚子里的虚空表明了一个意象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一堵墙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面不改色的表情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">装饰镜子简单的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两者的距离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只差一步之遥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把文字写进白墙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">批判语言的不恰当</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是推之一倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">变成一座长长的桥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">镜子里的内容</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
