➜湖北诗人木子：秋去（外三首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/418856270_100115135	52611
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/b642873938a345c8806cd5cb32a80cd1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝：秋去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月下思如箭，窗前泪若珠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孤灯沉夜露，玉影挽流苏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/442f3b37560243a781c3c13b0ec34678.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝：秋寒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄叶随风住，残枝裸露心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奈何生与死，独自倚词林。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ce529e6c7ac04c278a4b6472f7d182aa.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
